data.description: Welcome to 2430 Quincy Loop, Fairburn, GA! This charming home situated in a cul-de-sac boasts 4 bedrooms and 3 full baths, providing ample space for comfortable living. Enjoy the welcoming atmosphere with freshly painted interior, enhancing the home's aesthetic appeal. The downstairs features an open 2 story foyer with hardwood floors, a flex room that offers versatility to be transformed into an additional bedroom, catering to your evolving needs. Laminate flooring in the kitchen and family room. One A/C unit is 1 year old.  Entertain guests or gather in the spacious family room and dining room, providing the perfect setting for memorable moments. The bright, airy and spacious hallway upstairs offers extra space, an open layout with an abundance of natural sunlight. The spacious master bedroom features a sitting room for a private retreat and an opportunity to personalize the space to your needs.  This home offers convenience and close proximity to Trilith Movie Studios and Atlanta Metro Studios with only a 10 minute drive, shopping and dining in Fayetteville Pavilion, easy access to I-85 and to the Atlanta Hartsfield Airport.  **Ask us about the opportunity to get 100% Financing Available $0 Down Payment and NO PMI.**  Make this beautiful home with all it has to offer yours today!
